{"tid":2261951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浸大運動場冧鐵閘 壓傷男職員","createTime":"2020-10-28T16:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T17:22:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd06e41003eec093f6ba6c1cc3099435d3e8344","tid":2261951,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9PCtBYTf3gysOfxAo4mKc2XJsUg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YKETWF55ENESBHCPM6STIMDDXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9PCtBYTf3gysOfxAo4mKc2XJsUg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYKETWF55ENESBHCPM6STIMDDXM.jpg&h=e62f5026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上10時許，九龍塘聯福道浸會大學聯校運動中心，一幅3米闊2米高的鐵閘突然倒塌，一名浸大男職員走避不及遭倒下的鐵閘壓傷，幸未有大礙，傷者被救出時清醒，其後由救護員送院治理。倒下的鐵閘為車輛通道的活動門，通道晚上10米由職員負責關閉，鐵閘上有3個門鉸位，最頂的一個完全斷裂，懷疑鐵閘不勝負荷倒下壓傷職員，餘下兩個鉸位均出現生鏽情況，事故原因仍待查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201028/PH2H4BTNAFAYFOL6MFG2Z4KO4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201028%2FPH2H4BTNAFAYFOL6MFG2Z4KO4U%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=bdee36fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201028%2FPH2H4BTNAFAYFOL6MFG2Z4KO4U%2F&h=58f3e44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201028/PH2H4BTNAFAYFOL6MFG2Z4KO4U/</a>"},{"pid":"c753bd7e503b64c40ebaf524cb71ea21d39a8088","tid":2261951,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"佢都幾黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f839560f00ce7885df833fafd7ab7b1e0ae53c","tid":2261951,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"碎料 我城又冧過 